data.description: Welcome to Drexel Park Gardens featuring a lovely-end unit townhome 3 bedrooms with one bathroom, a beautiful garden with a back entrance to a one-car garage, and additional parking in the back of the home. Hardwood floors throughout the home. Gallery kitchen, gas heat, and full basement with washer and dryer included, spacious living, dining & kitchen & an abundance of natural light. The second floor has a generously-sized main bedroom with a ceiling fan, two additional bedrooms & bath with skylight. One of the property's best features is that it's an END UNIT with more land than all of the other homes on the block! Grass on the opposite side of the common driveway belongs to this property. HVAC, hot water heater, and the roof have been recently updated in the last 3 years
